                Banking & Financial Services            


Astute Solutions lands private equity investment, promises expansion




Jul 25, 2014, 12:22pm EDT






Industries & Tags


                    Banking & Financial Services,                 



                    Technology,                 



                    Career & Workplace,                 


            Mergers and Acquisitions,              

            Private equity             














