We are practical innovators. We design, make and customize innovative well construction products that help customers in the energy industry solve real-world problems.Headquartered in Houston, Rubicon has 20 offices worldwide including Aberdeen and Dubai, and local offices in Bogota, Calgary, Kazakhstan and Stavanger.Today, Rubicon is supplying its products to over 50 countries worldwide.
